            "isComplex": true,
            "level": {
                "value": 1
            },
            "reset": "<p>The trap deactivates once it no longer detects the presence of creatures in the room.</p>",
            "routine": "<p>(2 actions) The pillar Strides, following the track in the room. If the trap's track is broken, the pillar can still Stride, but its Speed is only 10 feet. The pillar cannot move at all if the track is destroyed. When the pillar moves, it deals [[/r (1d6+3)[fire]]] damage to any creatures whose space it moves through.</p>",
